{"tid":1187658,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"貿易戰大轉單 野村：台灣將獲佔GDP逾2％訂單 居世界第2","createTime":"2019-06-05T20:41:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T12:02:08.000Z","uid":141151,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5e1ee21eaba48e0353e27470c9f3b01e28bdc301","tid":1187658,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T20:41:42.000Z","msg":"貿易戰大轉單 野村：台灣將獲佔GDP逾2％訂單 居世界第2<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2811057\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2811057&d=HGsIALD6rBmJFWdd%2FklEluf4PGxNkgPyFAzKtVao6pc%3D&h=ecfd4134\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2811057&h=d55013a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2811057</a><br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕美中貿易戰改變全球供應鏈的趨勢越來越明顯，美國及中國紛紛將訂單轉移到別的國家，而日本金融機構「野村控股」調查發現，預估未來1年台灣獲得的新訂單價值約為台灣GDP的2.12%，佔比居世界第2，不過仍遠低於世界第1的越南，預估越南獲得的新訂單價值為該國GDP的7.9%。<br />\n《彭博》報導，該研究由野村控股的經濟學家Rob Subbaraman、Sonal Varma及Michael Loo所作成，調查對象為全球前50大經濟體，調查內容則為中美雙方分別課徵關稅的產品；結果顯示，獲得中美2國轉單佔該國GDP比例最高的國家，依序為越南、台灣、智利、馬來西亞及阿根廷。<br />\n<br />\n其中越南及台灣受惠於美國的訂單轉單，而其他3國則受惠於中國的訂單轉單；據調查，台灣獲得美國轉單約佔台灣GDP的1.94%，而獲得中國轉單佔比則為0.18%；越南獲得佔GDP約7.9%的訂單中，美國轉單就佔了約7.5%。<br />\n至於其他3國，智利獲得佔GDP約1.48%的訂單，其中中國轉單佔1.36%；馬來西亞獲得佔GDP約1.34%的訂單，其中中國轉單佔1.08%；而阿根廷獲得佔GDP約1.23%的訂單，其中中國轉單佔1.19%。<br />\n報導指出，這也反映了中美2國關稅戰造成訂單內容不同，對美國而言，需要轉單的產品中最首要的是電子產品，其次是家具及旅遊用品等；而對中國而言，需要轉單的產品則為黃豆、飛行器、穀物及棉花等。"},{"pid":"20266d72608f005e36c31625aa039cd806fa00b2","tid":1187658,"uid":55421,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T21:29:28.000Z","msg":"發大財 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"209e74399596c508ec24a7e40ca052f09f807162","tid":1187658,"uid":50310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T21:31:36.000Z","msg":"支持呀！<br />\n既然大陸工廠唔肯環保<br />\n索性令佢單都無得接<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86673305ded78d518c9e49c8cc65866de7dc1073","tid":1187658,"uid":57914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T21:44:46.000Z","msg":"無知一問，飛行器係咪即係Drone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d253644be1414d5dccc044dd26913cf326d76014","tid":1187658,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T05:30:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9935e4d3aaa9d27bb55ed2da6272c4ea6cd5704","tid":1187658,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T07:09:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc5105b7beffcbdd8e0c4adadd9848471d3ea5cf","tid":1187658,"uid":40588,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"86673305ded78d518c9e49c8cc65866de7dc1073","tid":1187658,"uid":57914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T21:44:46.000Z","msg":"無知一問，飛行器係咪即係Drone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T07:38:23.000Z","msg":"竹蜻蜓"},{"pid":"79aa9708ad9ec03590da1a48ee0b258122cb6bad","tid":1187658,"uid":11148,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T07:49:18.000Z","msg":"你睇下美國以前對支那幾撚好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以容許支那食盡全球訂單市場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n支那一有錢就妄想取代美國輸出共產獨裁主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ea4e4e81d3be12a5c5f86d149d6a530303956a6","tid":1187658,"uid":43309,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T07:51:18.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，阻你少少位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【民陣6.9反惡法遊行